# ğŸ•µï¸ Fake News Detection

An enhanced machine learning pipeline that classifies news articles as **REAL** or **FAKE** using TF-IDF vectorization and a Passive Aggressive Classifier.

---

## âœ¨ Features

- **Enhanced Text Preprocessing** â€” URL removal, HTML stripping, lowercasing, regex cleaning
- **Bigram TF-IDF Vectorization** â€” captures richer context than unigrams alone
- **Tuned PAC Model** â€” early stopping, stratified splits, log-normalization
- **Comprehensive Metrics** â€” accuracy, F1, precision, recall, confusion matrix, full classification report
- **Visualization** â€” auto-generated confusion matrix heatmap & metrics bar chart
- **Model Persistence** â€” save and reload trained model with `pickle`
- **Inference API** â€” `predict()` function with confidence score for single articles

